<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>يَا خشْمِ قِلْ لِلَمِعْتِدِي ... جْرُوح كان انِّكْ نِسِيْتْ<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>يَصْبِر وْنَاخِذْ ثَارَنَا ... الصبْح مَا هُو بَالْمِبِيْتْ<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>مِنْ فَوقِ خَيْلٍ مُكْرَمَاتْ ... مِنْ فَوْقِهِن بِعْتُ وْشَرَيْت<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
